\begin{picture}(-5,0)(2.5,0)
\put(44.52756,-195.9035){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}   As part of the end-of-semester project for the ALSD module, I have}
\put(44.52756,-216.7493){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}developed a comprehensive programming library designed to assist}
\put(44.52756,-237.5952){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}programmers in their work with numbers, strings, arrays, and matrices. }
\put(44.52756,-279.2869){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}      This library is structured with a collection of well-documented functions}
\put(44.52756,-300.1327){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}and procedures, each tailored to simplify complex operations and enhance}
\put(44.52756,-320.9785){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}efficiency.}
\put(44.52756,-362.6702){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}    The library aims to serve as a versatile toolkit for developers by providing}
\put(44.52756,-383.5161){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}solutions to common computational challenges. Every function and}
\put(44.52756,-404.3619){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}procedure is designed with clear objectives, well-defined inputs and}
\put(44.52756,-425.2078){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}outputs, and logical approaches to ensure clarity and ease of use.}

\put(44.52756,-295.3579){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}presented a personal challenge with string operations. Since this topic}
\put(44.52756,-316.2038){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}wasn't covered in lectures, I had to independently dive into learning and}
\put(44.52756,-337.0496){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}applying them. The skills acquired during this time were critical for the}
\put(44.52756,-357.8955){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}project’s success. By the final week of December 2024, I had mastered}
\put(44.52756,-378.7413){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}array operations and successfully incorporated them into the library.The}
\put(44.52756,-399.5872){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}matrices operations, along with the optional parts, were completed in}
\put(44.52756,-420.433){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{b}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}Junuary 2025, adding depth and complexity to the library with advanced}
\put(44.52756,-441.2788){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}functions like matrix inversion, determinant calculation, and LU}
\put(44.52756,-462.1247){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}decomposition.}
\put(44.52756,-503.8164){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}      The entire report was written piece by piece after completing each}
\put(44.52756,-524.6622){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}section, documenting the library’s development in detail. This project,}
\put(44.52756,-545.5081){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}which will be shared with professors on GitHub, is not only a reflection of}
\put(44.52756,-566.3539){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}my growth as a programmer but also a showcase of problem-solving, self-}
\put(44.52756,-587.1997){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}learning, and the application of theoretical knowledge to practical}
\put(44.52756,-608.0456){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}programming challenges.}
\put(44.52756,-649.7373){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}       I hope to share the knowledge  and  experience gained, while also}
\put(44.52756,-670.5831){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}receiving valuable feedback from professors and peers. I am confident that}
\put(44.52756,-691.429){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}the work done will be beneficial not only for my academic growth but also}
\put(44.52756,-712.2748){\fontsize{15.00067}{1}\usefont{T1}{cmr}{m}{n}\selectfont\color{color_29791}for future endeavors in the field of programming.}
\end{picture}
